data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Waterfron paradise living on Lake Tarpon! MANY tasteful updates to this quiet home. 3 BR 2 BA split plan. Kitchen opened up and remodled 2 years ago with granite counter tops cooking island hardwood cabinets and all new appliances. New engineered hardwood floors throught 4 years ago, HVAC 4 years ago, water softener 1 year, water heater 1 year, MBR remodeled 3 years ago, screen porch new screen 4 years, 2 newer wooden tuff sheds. Optional playground and boat ramp in the community. Owner had large pontoon boat tied to wood pilings in canal attached to tex deck.  Current owner has VA loan.
